<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Konfirmasi Hapus Data Siswa</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h2>Konfirmasi Hapus Data Siswa</h2>
        <p>Apakah Anda yakin ingin menghapus data siswa dengan NIS <%= data.NIS %>?</p>
        <form method="post" action="/delete/<%= data.NIS %>">
            <input type="submit" value="Ya" class="btn btn-danger">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Tidak</a>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
